WEBVTT

00:00:00.040 --> 00:00:03.760
[This talk contains mature content]

00:00:04.680 --> 00:00:10.496
My mother called this summer
to stage an intervention.

00:00:10.520 --> 00:00:16.496
She'd come across
a few snippets of my memoir,

00:00:16.520 --> 00:00:18.256
which wasn't even out yet,

00:00:18.280 --> 00:00:19.480
and she was concerned.

00:00:21.040 --> 00:00:22.736
It wasn't the sex.

00:00:22.760 --> 00:00:24.536
(Laughter)

00:00:24.560 --> 00:00:27.680
It was the language that disturbed her.

